     CLR         CM,B      IFEQ '*'
     CLR         FI,B      OREQ *BLANK
     CLR         B         ADD  30        Y       20
     CLR                   MOVE '1'       *IN,Y
     CLR                   END
     CLR                   END
     CLR         STEP01    TAG
